text: Bridport is a town near the A35 road in Dorset, England. It is near the coast at the western end of Chesil Beach. In 2006 West Dorset district was named 10th best place to live in the UK.best and worst places to live 2006 The town is twinned with Saint-Vaast-la-Hougue, France. ==References== Category:Towns in Dorset Category:West Dorset
title: Bridport
